v0.2.0-alpha - "Thumb-Centered Gesture Control"

Features:
- Thumb-centered pinch gesture detection between thumb and index finger
- Drawing follows thumb position instead of index finger for more stability
- Customizable thresholds (current: 0.07 for pinch, 0.10 for release)
- Visual feedback with distance measurement
- Settings panel for gesture configuration
- Hysteresis and stabilization to prevent flickering
- Simplified ROI tracking focused on thumb position

Date: April 25, 2025